# =============================================================================
# .dockerignore — keep the build context small and reproducible.
# Reduces COPY time, image size, and the risk of leaking secrets.
# =============================================================================

# .NET build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/publish/
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.userosscache
**/*.userprefs
**/*.sln.docstates
**/[Dd]ebug/
**/[Rr]elease/
**/[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*

# Test artifacts
**/TestResults/
**/coverage*/
**/coverage/
**/.coverage
**/*.coverage
**/quality-reports/
**/.stryker-config/

# IDE / editor
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Git & CI metadata
**/.git/
**/.gitattributes
**/.gitignore
**/.github/
**/.gitlab-ci.yml
**/.azure-pipelines.yml

# Local secrets & state
**/secrets.json
**/appsettings.*.Local.json
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/*.pfx
**/*.p12
**/*.key

# User-uploaded data (recreated by the container at runtime)
**/AppData/uploads/
**/AppData/clamav-db/
**/AppData/logs/

# Documentation (rebuilt from source)
README.md
CHANGELOG.md
code-quality-report.md
SECURITY-AUDIT.md
LICENSE-CODE
**/*.md

# Node / front-end tooling (not used in this project, but safe to ignore)
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# Other
**/StakeholderDocs/
**/specs/
**/scripts/
**/.agents/
**/.specify/
**/.config/
**/skills-lock.json
